                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-625-18720819 t18720819-625-punishment-62"></join>Twelve Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">STRADLING</hi>.—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18720819-625-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18720819-625-verdict-3" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18720819-625-verdict-3" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
He received a good character.—<rs id="t18720819-625-punishment-63" type="punishmentDescription">
